---
title: Mediterranean Beef Meatballs & Tzatziki with Wedges & Greek Salad
description: With favourite ingredients from the sun-soaked Mediterranean region, this bowl is supercharged with flavour. From the creamy tzatziki to the feta-studded Greek salad, it's a dinner to remember.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mediterranean-meatballs-tzatziki-8017905b.jpg
